<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-20481] Various improvements and bug fixes in constraint framework</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-20481</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;fix 1 - evaluate constraints upon satisfaction check using types of logical function it uses instead of column types&lt;br/&gt;
fix 2 - refactor code, remove irrelevant leftovers&lt;br/&gt;
fix 3 - support specification of a constraint when altering a table and adding a column&lt;br/&gt;
fix 4 - harden NOT_NULL constraint&lt;br/&gt;
fix 5 - for now, support only frozen collections, effectively only not_null constraint&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
